title: Circus Of Sound - Ohm (2008)
description:
Circus Of Sound by Ohm

Circus Of Soudn is the third studio album of the band Ohm, fronted by Chris Poland (former Megadeth guitarist). It was released on August 26th, 2008 on Tone Center Records.

Personnel
Chris Poland - Guitarist, Engineer, Producer
Robertino Pagliari - Bassist
Joel Tayler - Drums (Tracks 1-3)
Frank Briggs - Drums (Tracks 4-7)
Kofi Baker - Drums (Tracks 8-14)
